Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Sorry, Princess Twilight!\NThat was meant for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,INCOMING!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Toola Roola! Coconut Cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was meant for\Nmy ex-friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your ex-friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my ex-friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, friendship\Nisn't always easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no doubt\Nit's worth fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Awwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. That sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. No. Uh uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.47,0:01:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't judge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the friendship journal\Nmy friends and I used to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's filled with all the\Nthings we've learned!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... "friendship\Nisn't always easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no doubt it's\Nworth fighting for."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll.. judge a book by its\Ncover just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a surprise for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Twilight? Do I\Nneed to prepare myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so smelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Is this our old\Nfriendship journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen this\Nthing in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooo-wee, it's lookin' a\Nlittle uh, overripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a smooshed apple\Nin Applejack's lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy's lessons are so\Nsmall, you can barely read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I.. uh.. wanted to leave\Nroom for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't even\Nknow what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is called\Ncalligraphy, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to make words,\Nat least make them fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got a\Nlittle aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with your friendship\Nlessons, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I learn something,\NI learn it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I found Pinkie's page.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee hee! Well, I\Nam surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't\Nthe only surprise..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Ta da! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I decided to\Nmake one for each of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazin'!\NA perfect copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned the spell years ago\Nwhen I needed to make copies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of a certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...manifesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Even better than\Na perfect copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd forgotten all\Nabout this lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! Remember this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From when I helped Daring Do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Never underestimate\Nthe power of friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,who've always got your back."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, Cheese Sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Party cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Birthaversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After Twilight\Nremembered the journal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I had so much fun reading all\Nthe stuff you've all learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had to have\Nmy own copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And that brings me to the\Nsecond part of the surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you girls feel\Nabout making our journal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,available for everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can get these lessons\Ninto other ponies' hooves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe they'll benefit from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think\Nthat's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in! YAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We always said we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha, I'm awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, uh, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Toola Roola: {\i1}No! I don't want to{\i0}\N{\i1}play with you anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? You love\Nplaying hopscotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No,{\i1} you{\i0} do. Because\Nyou always win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Twilight: Hey, girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't help but overhear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You might want to\Ntake a breather,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe read Rainbow Dash's\Nchapter on Rainbow Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom: {\i1}Thanks, Twilight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The friendship journal's\Nmakin' us super popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We were thinkin' of\Nputting together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a Cutie Mark Summer Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everypony's definitely\Ngonna sign up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be awesome! Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A Cutie Mark Camp\Nis a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but the purpose\Nof the journal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't supposed to\Nbe marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope those foals\Nactually learn something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from our lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They will. I'm sure ponies all\Nacross Equestria will--woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here all the way\Nfrom Fillydelphia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,because we got copies of\Nyour friendship journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your favorite\Nfriendship--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you sign them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Uh, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you\Nthink of the lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we haven't read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,These are keepsakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta keep them\Nin mint condition. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was worth the trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twilight, I'm\Nsure lots of other ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,are being inspired to\Nbe better friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I for one found the\Njournal terribly illuminating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm seeing sides of these\Nponies I didn't know were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish they'd\Nleft Rarity out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She clearly doesn't belong in\Nthat book with the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does she think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly she did a\Nfine job setting up the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville Days Celebration,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but does she really\Nbelieve it was a success
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,just because of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what\Nshe was saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Poor Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She overheard all the mean\Nthings those ponies were saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a\Nchat with these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Our journals are everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie! I've got to--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies keep stopping\Nby to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,my entries are hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had somepony come all\Nthe way from Las Pegasus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to say how much he\Nliked my lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so glad to hear\Nsomeponies are being inspired
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by the journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey look! There's Pinkie\NPie, the funny one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Giggly feedback\Nis the best kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least you're\Ngetting a positive reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this whole journal\Nthing really upset her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that wasn't\Neven funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Well, I guess\NI'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Bye, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Classic Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's even funnier\Nin real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've known\Nme for years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash: Maybe it's\Ntime to call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I ripped out all the Twilight\NSparkle lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause they were getting in\Nthe way of the good ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you\Nskipped the lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all had\Nvaluable experiences!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, here's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys talk to\NTwilight for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can get back to things\Nlike working and napping and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,well, pretty much anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, we don't want to\Nhear her boring lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell us again about\Nwhen you met Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't we already\Ncovered that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple dozen times?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get enough of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you don't want\Nto disappoint your fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. It's just that I, uh,\Nreally need to get those
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,stormclouds back\Nin their.... pens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! We'll come along and you\Ncan tell us the story there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Rainbow Dash!\NRainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We want answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're\Nentitled to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to know why\NFluttershy keeps learning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the same thing over\Nand over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be assertive, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I've learned\Nmore than she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I be in the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? Are you\Nattacking my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because you want\Nto be in a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. I've\Ngot this, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! I{\i1} am{\i0}\Nmore assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes, it took me\Na while to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you honestly say that\Nyou could learn something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,one time and completely\Nchange who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You're way different from\Nthe Fluttershy in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\NI feel about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like\Neverypony in Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is missing the friendship part\Nof the friendship journals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I'm creating\Na gown, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stress-sewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress-sewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I overheard those\Ntwo at the cafe,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly understood why
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been getting\Ncancellations for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are ponies\Ncancelling their orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because.. nopony\Nlikes me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're boycotting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure if I go out there\Nand talk to those ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll see that they're\Nbeing unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a hundred blankets\Nand I need 'em now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away, Pony\Nwho still likes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need nothin' fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm popular, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm popular and I\Ndon't like it one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead, I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, who are\Nall these ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They call themselves "the\NSweet Apple Admirers."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they read\Nmy journal entries
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and they felt like a\Npart of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they want to actually\Nbecome part of the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your journal entries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know, all the stuff\Nabout how friends are like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,family and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you get rid of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And kick out my own family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Smith!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, let me help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,YEEEEEE-HAAWWWW!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I wish we'd never\Nreleased that journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I just left Rarity; I\Nthink she's doing better and-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Window staring, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that bad at\NSweet Apple Acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was\Ndoing something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How could our friendship\Njournal have led to so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,anti-friendship!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight, it's\Nnot your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't had the big\Nidea to make copies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,none of this would\Nbe happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I made life\Nawful for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I really think you're\Nbeing too hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know where else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got so much cookin' and\Ncleanin' and familyin' to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't got time\Nfor anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At least ponies aren't\Nlaughing every time you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even I want to be\Nfunny all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, my days\Nof hilariosityness... ness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,are OVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you've got problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm awesome but I can't\Neven go to the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without somepony trying to\Ntell me how cool I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...Rarity, what\Nare you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My emotions, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress couture!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'm going to\Ndo if I have to defend myself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Er.. sorry, Darling.\NForce of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so maybe they are\Nhaving a hard time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you\Ndid anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Releasing the\Njournal was my idea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and it backfired in ways I\Ncould never have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everypony else's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just focusing\Non the wrong things and-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with the Canterlot\NChronicle, quick question...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say to ponies\Nwho wonder why you moved
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to Ponyville in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved here to learn\Nabout friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the\Njournal even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It took some time for me\Nto get the hang of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was each of these\Nponies standing next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who taught me the lessons\Nin those journals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And Fluttershy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it was all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've learned so much\Nfrom--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is, some\Nponies would argue that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't seem believable that\Nthe six of you would be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Believable?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I read this journal cover\Nto cover and I have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,your character would have\Nbeen much more interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if she'd stayed in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My character!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We are real ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This journal is a\Nrecord of things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that actually\Nhappened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We made mistakes and\Nwe learned from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really supposed to\Nbelieve she learned anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,she wrote in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you\Ngotta be Team Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the only one who didn't\Nreally need to learn anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because she was already so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight was better\Nbefore she got wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy is just\Nso painfully shy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to relate.\NI mean, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Pinkie Pie and\NApplejack related or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,LISTEN TO ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I never claimed to{\i0}\N{\i1} be perfect ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My mistakes are all{\i0}\N{\i1} written in ink ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ None of us claimed{\i0}\N{\i1} to be perfect ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And it's sad that's{\i0}\N{\i1} what you all think. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Our flaws help to make{\i0}\N{\i1} us special ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ They bond us and{\i0}\N{\i1} keep us strong ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Our flaws are what{\i0}\N{\i1} brought us together ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So stop acting like{\i0}\N{\i1} something's wrong. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're not flawless{\i0}\N{\i1} We're work in progress ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We've got dents and{\i0}\N{\i1} we've got quirks ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But it's our flaws that{\i0}\N{\i1} make us work, yeah ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're not flawless{\i0}\N{\i1} We're work in progress ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So tell me what flaws{\i0}\N{\i1} you've got, too ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ cause I still like{\i0}\N{\i1} what's flawed about you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ They say I'm a big shot ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That my ego's the{\i0}\N{\i1} size of a whale ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ My confidence comes off{\i0}\N{\i1} as cocky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But it gives me the{\i0}\N{\i1} courage to fail. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sure I can be a drama queen{\i0}\N{\i1} A bit stuck up, it's true ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And I can be too{\i0}\N{\i1} eager to please ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's such thing as being{\i0}\N{\i1} too honest too cause... ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're not flawless{\i0}\N{\i1} We're work in progress ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We've got dents and{\i0}\N{\i1} we've got quirks ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But it's our flaws that{\i0}\N{\i1} make us work, yeah ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're not flawless{\i0}\N{\i1} We're work in progress ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So tell me what{\i0}\N{\i1} flaws you got too ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ cause I still like what's{\i0}\N{\i1} flawed about you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Ponies think I'm all{\i0}\N{\i1} bubbles and laughter ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That I don't seem sincere ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I might joke around a{\i0}\N{\i1} little too much ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But I'm just so{\i0}\N{\i1} happy you're here. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ It took me a while{\i0}\N{\i1} to be confident ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ To really come out{\i0}\N{\i1} of my shell ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But no pony has{\i0}\N{\i1} to be perfect ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ By now don't you know us{\i0}\N{\i1} so well because, yeah ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're not flawless{\i0}\N{\i1} We're work in progress ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We've got dents and{\i0}\N{\i1} we've got quirks ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But it's our flaws that{\i0}\N{\i1} make us work yeah ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're not flawless{\i0}\N{\i1} We're work in progress ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So tell me what{\i0}\N{\i1} flaws you got too ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Cause I still like{\i0}\N{\i1} what's flawed about you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us ever\Nclaimed to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Without our flaws,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there wouldn't be any\Nfriendship lessons to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Without our flaws...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,... there probably wouldn't\Nbe any friendships at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So that just\Nhappened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls! I found two ponies\Nwho have something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... we just wanted to say\Nthank you to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Our friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,well, we were having trouble\Nuntil we read your journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It showed us that friends can go\Nthrough all sorts of tough times
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and come through\Nstronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made us better friends\Nthan we've ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can't tell you how\Nmuch it means to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had a tough\Ncouple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But knowing we've helped\Nfillies like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes everything we've\Nbeen through worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fads come and go;\Nfriendship is forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are worse things than\Nnot being able to do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,without being told I'm awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't change the way\Nother ponies think about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can change how\Nwe let it affect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how we don't\Nlet it affect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Heh. Go ahead. Laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Reckon we still have to\Ndeal with them, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in the friendship\Nmoment, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They can wait a little longer.
